<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 09:15:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>隐藏了几个世纪的中国珍宝终于看到了一天的光芒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/hidden-centuries-chinese-treasures-finally-see-light-day-2025-02-21/</link><description>清朝漆面板上饰有玉米和玛瑙的清漆漆面板在薄雾笼罩的景观中描绘了道教神灵，这是成千上万的人工制品中的成千上万的文物中，从中国的博物馆存储中撤出，有一天，甚至有一天都向世界展示。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 08:29:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/hidden-centuries-chinese-treasures-finally-see-light-day-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>VDMA说，2024年的德国机械出口下降，VDMA说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-machinery-exports-decline-2024-amid-feeble-demand-vdma-says-2025-02-21/</link><description>VDMA行业协会在周五的一份声明中说，德国机械工程出口与2024年的生产相符，并补充说，经济和结构性挑战在全球范围内削弱了需求。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 08:27:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-machinery-exports-decline-2024-amid-feeble-demand-vdma-says-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>BYD的Fangchengbao推出了具有高级自动驾驶功能的插电式混合动力车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byds-fangchengbao-launches-plug-in-hybrid-with-advanced-autonomous-driving-2025-02-21/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商Byd的越野品牌Fangchengbao周五推出了其插电式混合动力SUV BAO 5的智能版本。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 07:26:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byds-fangchengbao-launches-plug-in-hybrid-with-advanced-autonomous-driving-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国说，他将与美国财政部长的视频通话副总理</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-vice-premier-he-lifeng-will-have-video-call-with-us-treasury-2025-02-21/</link><description>外交部周五说，中国的副总理他将与美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）进行视频呼吁，以在两国之间在经济领域中传达重要问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 07:25:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-vice-premier-he-lifeng-will-have-video-call-with-us-treasury-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>意大利监管机构探测Stellantis，VW，特斯拉和Byd，EV消费者信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-antitrust-agency-opens-probe-stellantis-volkswagen-tesla-byd-misleading-2025-02-21/</link><description>意大利的反托拉斯机构周五表示，正在调查Byd，Stellantis，Tesla和Volkswagen，因为据称对消费者的电动汽车性能误导了消费者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 07:22:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-antitrust-agency-opens-probe-stellantis-volkswagen-tesla-byd-misleading-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>商业航空公司警告说，中国海军在澳大利亚举行现场火灾练习时</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/commercial-airlines-warned-chinese-navy-holds-live-fire-exercise-off-australia-2025-02-21/</link><description>航空公司周五在中国通知澳大利亚通知澳大利亚的人民解放军海军将在新南威尔士州海岸举行的国际水域中，这是罕见的事件，这是澳大利亚和新西兰之间的飞行道路。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 06:22:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/commercial-airlines-warned-chinese-navy-holds-live-fire-exercise-off-australia-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>电动运输集团敦促欧盟不要简化二氧化碳排放规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/electric-transport-groups-urge-eu-not-ease-co2-emission-rules-2025-02-21/</link><description>欧洲联盟应拒绝欧洲汽车制造商的推动削弱2025 CO2汽车排放目标和相关罚款。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 06:08:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/electric-transport-groups-urge-eu-not-ease-co2-emission-rules-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国希望成为乌克兰和平缔造者与特朗普和贸易的目标相撞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-hopes-be-ukraine-peacemaker-collide-with-its-goals-trump-trade-2025-02-21/</link><description>虽然北京希望被视为全球和平缔造者，但它正在寻求这样做而不会产生成本或冒险，尤其是当他们可能破坏与莫斯科的联系时，它依赖于廉价的能源。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 05:31:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-hopes-be-ukraine-peacemaker-collide-with-its-goals-trump-trade-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国的监管宽松希望使海上股票筹款的前景更加明亮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulatory-easing-hopes-brighten-outlook-offshore-equity-fundraising-2025-02-21/</link><description>中国公司正在利用北京对私人公司的支持和DeepSeek的受欢迎程度的希望所推动的投资者情绪。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 05:07:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulatory-easing-hopes-brighten-outlook-offshore-equity-fundraising-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>利润增长后，Stanchart股票达到了近十年的高峰，1.5 bln回购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-reports-18-rise-annual-profit-roughly-line-with-estimates-2025-02-21/</link><description>《标准特许》宣布了周五的新股票回购新的15亿美元回购，此前其年度利润增长了18％的财富业务增长和市场部门的出色表现，将其股票推向了近十年的高价。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 04:32:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-reports-18-rise-annual-profit-roughly-line-with-estimates-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国刺激希望的铁矿石头可获得每周增益的增益，希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/iron-ore-heads-weekly-gain-brightening-demand-outlook-china-stimulus-hopes-2025-02-21/</link><description>铁矿石期货价格在周五在四个多月份以来上涨至最高水平，并获得了每周的收益，因为钢铁消费的迹象使中国顶级消费者的需求前景更加明亮，希望能够恢复更多刺激。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 04:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/iron-ore-heads-weekly-gain-brightening-demand-outlook-china-stimulus-hopes-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>卢比奥说，特朗普，普京的会议取决于结束乌克兰战争的进步。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-putin-meeting-depends-progress-toward-ending-ukraine-war-says-rubio-2025-02-21/</link><description>美国国务卿马可·卢比奥（Marco Rubio）周四表示，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）与俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）之间的一次会议“很大程度上取决于我们是否可以在乌克兰结束战争方面取得任何进展。”</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 03:50:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-putin-meeting-depends-progress-toward-ending-ukraine-war-says-rubio-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>独家：ABRDN在与CITIC部门开展中国资产管理公司的会谈中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/abrdn-launch-china-asset-management-venture-with-citic-unit-sources-say-2025-02-21/</link><description>艾伯特（Abrdn）正在与CITIC BANK进行高级会谈，以在中国开设一家资产管理合资企业，因为这家英国公司希望加强其在世界第二大经济体中的业务，这是对此事的知识。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 03:33:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/abrdn-launch-china-asset-management-venture-with-citic-unit-sources-say-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国的“ NE ZHA 2”动画大片燃料民族主义者，好莱坞敌意</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/chinas-ne-zha-2-animated-blockbuster-fuels-nationalist-pride-hollywood-hostility-2025-02-21/</link><description>随着“ NE ZHA 2”破碎的票房记录，中国动画电影讲述了一个神话般的男孩，具有神奇的力量，引发了民族自豪感，现在对竞争对手好莱坞奉献的敌意，例如最新的《美国队长》。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 03:04:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/chinas-ne-zha-2-animated-blockbuster-fuels-nationalist-pride-hollywood-hostility-2025-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国军方说，它驱车驶离斯普拉特群岛附近的菲律宾飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-military-drove-away-philippine-aircraft-near-spratly-islands-2025-02-21/</link><description>中国军方表示，周四，它警告并开车驶离了三架菲律宾飞机，这些飞机“非法侵入”进入了斯普拉特群岛附近的空域。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 02:51:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-military-drove-away-philippine-aircraft-near-spratly-islands-2025-02-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>